### CRM - Field Definitions
### Merchants define custom fields for their contact types

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@merchantToken =eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhY2NvdW50SWQiOiI2OTkyMTQ5YTYwZWUxYWE0ZjA4ODlhYmQiLCJlbWFpbCI6InRlbWkuZGFyYW1vbGFAa2loYXNsLmNvbSIsInJvbGUiOiJtZXJjaGFudCIsImlhdCI6MTc3Mjc5Nzg0NSwiZXhwIjoxNzcyOTcwNjQ1fQ.A0aFx_gT-I3zTO7E99R3aB9awzZEuWNgCb4NVC4-6wc
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/fields
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Industry/Profession",
  "type": "text"
}

### Create custom field - Select type
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/fields
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Preferred Contact Method",
  "type": "select",
  "options": ["Email", "Phone", "SMS", "WhatsApp"]
}

### Create custom field - Date type
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/fields
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Last Purchase Date",
  "type": "date"
}

### Get all field definitions (system + custom)
GET {{baseUrl}}/crm/fields
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}

### Get single field definition
GET {{baseUrl}}/crm/fields/695a4573d9b1b90a9aa12d4a
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}

### Update custom field
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/crm/fields/695a4573d9b1b90a9aa12d4a
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "How to Reach You",
  "options": ["Email", "Phone", "SMS", "WhatsApp", "In-Person"]
}

### Delete custom field
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/crm/fields/695a456ed9b1b90a9aa12d48
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}

### Error - Try to create field with system field name (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/fields
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "First Name",
  "type": "text"
}

### Error - Create select field without options (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/fields
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Customer Status",
  "type": "select"
}
